                        <span>Oxo Glomma</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="deltaker">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" style="fill: rgba(255, 255, 255);transform: ;msFilter:;"><path d="M7.5 6.5C7.5 8.981 9.519 11 12 11s4.5-2.019 4.5-4.5S14.481 2 12 2 7.5 4.019 7.5 6.5zM20 21h1v-1c0-3.859-3.141-7-7-7h-4c-3.86 0-7 3.141-7 7v1h17z"></path></svg>
